<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8">
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      We received a request to reset the password for your <%= @token.data[:address] %> account. To reset your password, please click the link below:
    </p>
    <p>
      <%= link_to "Reset Your OrgPad Password", password_reset_url(token: @token.to_param) %>
    </p>
    <p>
      If you think it’s a mistake, just ignore this email.
    </p>
    <p>
      OrgPad is a convenient tool to chart and profile your company. Use it to clarify your team structure, your products, your goals, and become transparent. Transparency benefits your teams, your partners, and your investors.
    </p>
    <p>
      OrgPad is always free to use. If you have questions, want a product tour, or just want to talk about OrgPad, simply reply to this email or write to <%= mail_to 'team@orgpad.com' %>
    </p>
    <p>
      We’re happy to have you on OrgPad!
      <br>
      — Team OrgPad
    </p>    
  </body>
</html>
